   668→// DeltaAggregatedResources is not implemented.
   669→// Instead, Generators may send only updates/add, with Delete indicated by an empty spec.
   670→// This works if both ends follow this model. For example EDS and the API generator follow this
   671→// pattern.
   672→//
   673→// The delta protocol changes the request, adding unsubscribe/subscribe instead of sending full
   674→// list of resources. On the response it adds 'removed resources' and sends changes for everything.
   675→func (s *DiscoveryServer) DeltaAggregatedResources(stream discovery.AggregatedDiscoveryService_DeltaAggregatedResourcesServer) error {
   676→	return s.StreamDeltas(stream)
   677→}
